"Ether",
"Find My Way",
"Next 2 Me",
"Roll it Up",
"Shine"

]}

/>

<Listen

spotify="https://open.spotify.com/album/351UcYemx684zBP8be3P0M?si=DiiYapkOQtupyC4mvDUhKg"

apple="https://music.apple.com/za/album/17-17-ep/1734185756"

